short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple Extension that allows you to manage files on ClickUp

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Simple Chrome Extension that allows users to manage their documents on Clickup, users can upload, download, create and delete folders/documents accordingly which helps in saving them tons of time. 
This extension also serves as a record keeper, easy to share and simple UI for faster usability.
